on of form in space, on a two-dimensional surface.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Julie Karpodines','','publish','closed','closed','','julie-karpodines','','','2014-04-06 14:55:56','2014-04-06 14:55:56','',0,'http://theroadgallery.com/?post_type=artists&#038;p=152',7,'artists','',0),(154,2,'2014-01-03 22:40:56','2014-01-03 22:40:56','','woman standing_70.5x60_The Road Gallery','','inherit','open','open','','woman-standing_70-5x60_the-road-gallery','','','2014-01-03 22:40:56','2014-01-03 22:40:56','',152,'http://theroadgallery.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/woman-standing_70.5x60_The-Road-Gallery.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(155,2,'2014-01-03 22:43:39','2014-01-03 22:43:39','<strong>Year: </strong>2011\r\n\r\n<strong>Height:</strong> 70.5\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Width:</strong> 60\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Medium:</strong> Oil on canvas','Woman Standing','','publish','open','open','','womanstanding','','','2014-01-04 00:31:18','2014-01-04 00:31:18','',0,'http://theroadgallery.com/?p=155',436,'post','',0),(160,2,'2014-01-04 00:30:15','2014-01-04 00:30:15','<strong>Year:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\n<strong>Height: </strong>46\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Width: </strong>35\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Medium:</strong> Oil on canvas','Bridge #1','','publish','open','open','','bridge-1','','','2014-01-04 00:30:15','2014-01-04 00:30:15','',0,'http://theroadgallery.com/?p=160',435,'post','',0),(161,2,'2014-01-04 00:29:57','2014-01-04 00:29:57','','bridge #1_46X35_The Road Gallery','','inherit','open','open','','bridge-1_46x35_the-road-gallery','','','2014-01-04 00:29:57','2014-01-04 00:29:57','',160,'http://theroadgallery.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bridge-1_46X35_The-Road-Gallery.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(165,2,'2014-01-04 00:34:18','2014-01-04 00:34:18','<strong>Year:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\n<strong>Height: </strong>48\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Width: </strong>60\"\r\n\r\n<strong>Medium:</strong> Oil on canvas','Man and Dog','','publish','open','open','','man-and-dog','','','2014-01-04 00:34:18','2014-01-04 00:34:18','',0